# Changelog

All notable changes to this project will be documented in this file.

The format is based on [Keep a Changelog](https://keepachangelog.com/en/1.1.0/),
and this project adheres to [Semantic Versioning](https://semver.org/spec/v2.0.0.html).
## [version] - year-month-day
### Added
### Changed
### Deprecated
### Removed
### Fixed
### Security

## [0.5.0] - 2025-03-11
### Added

 - fully implemented Tests to check the status of modules when building
 - implementation of additional boundary resistance between differing cell materials
 - implementation of Neumann boundary conditions

### Changed
 - the conditions of some if statements to increase robustness
 - the format of the output file's name

### Removed
 - legacy test files
 - some utility files pushed by mistake



## [0.4.0] - 2024-03-21
### Added

 - Added ability to specify the range of cells that are written to output file.
 - Added ability to specifiy kappa boundary at 1x,1y,1z and nx,ny,nz 
 - Comments

### Changed

 - Changed the format of the system input geometry and heating and merged them.

### Removed
 - Source parameter in mat.in 
### Fixed

 - General formatting

## [0.3.0] - 2024-03-05

### Added

 - Cattaneo
 - 'Volz' heating

### Fixed
 
 - General code tidy
